      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and affordable daily driver? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! It shows some honest wear from its time on the road, but it remains a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a practical car with plenty of life left in it.",
      "price": 17000.0,
