    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the body panels are perfectly aligned with no dings or scratches. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the upholstery is unmarked, and all electronic features function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, offering a driving experience that is as smooth and quiet as a brand-new model. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standard.",
      "price": 48500.0,
