    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point technical inspection to ensure optimal mechanical integrity and roadworthiness. The exterior retains its professional finish, complemented by an interior that has been preserved with meticulous care. Designed for the driver who demands both reliability and a refined aesthetic, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity within its segment. We invite you to schedule a private viewing to appreciate the caliber of this offering.",
      "price": 36500.0,
