      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, it drives like a dream and still looks great! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with someone new. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes the Getrag six-speed manual transmission for a pure tactile connection. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS system has been serviced to maintain peak variable valve timing performance. The suspension retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with crisp turn-in and balanced damping. While the aesthetic reflects its use as a true driver's car, the drivetrain and variable M differential lock are robust, making this a turn-key performance machine.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
