    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained example that perfectly balances performance and practicality. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, with only minor road wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions flawlessly. Under the hood, this vehicle has been treated to a rigorous maintenance schedule, ensuring the engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision. It\u2019s a reliable, eye-catching car that\u2019s ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 32500.0,
